oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Will Fussner Stock Company Ledger: Sheet No. 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Hatch record for the Will Fussner Stock Company May 1924 to May 1928. Lists folio number, dates, items, itemized debits, total debits, and credits. Hatch printed posters for Will Fussner from 1924 to 1928.
